headline: Do Billionaires Ken Griffin and Izzy Englander Know Something About Palantir That Wall Street Doesn't?
summary: Griffin's and Englander's hedge funds bought Palantir shares hand over fist in Q1.  The two billionaires' options strategies might align them more closely with the consensus Wall Street take on Palantir than meets the eye.  Only one S&P 500 stock has outperformed Palantir Technologies (NASDAQ: PLTR) so far this year.
